      <guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.fourpoundbrain.com/?p=211</guid>
      <description>In this Filtrete air filter review, we&amp;#8217;ll cover the various filtration products offered by 3M and discuss how they can improve the quality of air in your home. 3M makes a wide variety of great products, and the Filtrete air filters are no exception. The Filtrete air filter lineup features electrostatically-charged technology for forced air [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/four-pound-brain/Four_Pound_Brain-Filtrete_Air_Filter_Review.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>In this Filtrete air filter review, we&#8217;ll cover the various filtration products offered by 3M and discuss how they can improve the quality of air in your home. 3M makes a wide variety of great products, and the Filtrete air filters are no exception.</p>
<p>The Filtrete air filter lineup features electrostatically-charged technology for forced air heating and cooling systems, as well as media air cleaning systems. Let&#8217;s take a look at the different options available.</p>
<h2>High Performance 1&#8243; Filters</h2>
<p>These are designed to capture at least 90% of the large airborne particles from the air that passes through the filter. They feature a microparticle rating of 1200 or higher and even capture smog, smoke, and particles carrying viruses.</p>
<h2>Air Cleaning 1&#8243; Filters</h2>
<p>Featuring a microparticle performance rating of 700 to 1000, these non-electrostatic filters help to eliminate microscopic allergens such as smoke and dust, as well as larger ones like pet dander and mold spores.</p>
<h2>High Air Flow 1&#8243; Filters</h2>
<p>Ideal for high-velocity equipment, these filters have a microparticle rating of 200 to 600 and are extremely effective at reducing pet dander, pollen, household dust, and mold spores.</p>
<h2>Media Air Cleaner 4&#8243; Filters</h2>
<p>Specifically designed for whole house air cleaners, these filters carry a 1550 microparticle rating and capture dust mite debris, pollen, and mold spores.</p>
<p>Hopefully this Filtrete air filter review has given you a better picture of the different options offered by 3M. Regardless of the filter you choose, we&#8217;re pretty confident that you&#8217;ll notice a difference in the overall air quality in your home.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
