      <title>How to See Amsterdam in 3 Hours</title>
      <link>http://www.fourpoundbrain.com/how-to-see-amsterdam-in-3-hours/</link>
      <comments>http://www.fourpoundbrain.com/how-to-see-amsterdam-in-3-hours/#comments</comments>
